INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2026-05-13 07:12:39','2026-05-13 07:12:39','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start writing!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Hello world!','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2026-05-13 07:12:39','2026-05-13 07:12:39','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/?p=1',0,'post','',1),
(2,1,'2026-05-13 07:12:39','2026-05-13 07:12:39','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>...or something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sample Page','','publish','closed','open','','sample-page','','','2026-05-13 07:12:39','2026-05-13 07:12:39','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),
(4,0,'2026-05-13 07:13:47','2026-05-13 07:13:47','<!-- wp:page-list /-->','Navigation','','publish','closed','closed','','navigation','','','2026-05-13 07:13:47','2026-05-13 07:13:47','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/navigation/',0,'wp_navigation','',0),
(6,0,'2026-05-13 09:20:43','2026-05-13 09:20:43','<label> Your name\n    [text* your-name autocomplete:name] </label>\n\n<label> Your email\n    [email* your-email autocomplete:email] </label>\n\n<label> Subject\n    [text* your-subject] </label>\n\n<label> Your message (optional)\n    [textarea your-message] </label>\n\n[submit \"Submit\"]\n[_site_title] \"[your-subject]\"\n[_site_title] <wordpress@zhongming.local>\nFrom: [your-name] [your-email]\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis is a notification that a contact form was submitted on your website ([_site_title] [_site_url]).\n[_site_admin_email]\nReply-To: [your-email]\n\n0\n0\n\n[_site_title] \"[your-subject]\"\n[_site_title] <wordpress@zhongming.local>\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis email is a receipt for your contact form submission on our website ([_site_title] [_site_url]) in which your email address was used. If that was not you, please ignore this message.\n[your-email]\nReply-To: [_site_admin_email]\n\n0\n0\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nPlease fill out this field.\nThis field has a too long input.\nThis field has a too short input.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe uploaded file is too large.\nThere was an error uploading the file.','Contact form 1','','publish','closed','closed','','contact-form-1','','','2026-05-13 09:20:43','2026-05-13 09:20:43','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&p=6',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),
(398,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:08','2026-05-14 03:13:08','The Standard Indoor P2.5 series is designed for fixed installation where high pixel density and superior color reproduction are required. It features a lightweight cabinet design that simplifies installation and maintenance.\n\nWith a pixel pitch of 2.5mm and a pixel density of 160,000 dot/m², it provides crisp visuals for close-range viewing. The cabinet resolution of 256×192px ensures high-fidelity playback of 2K/4K content.\n\nPerfect for corporate lobbies, high-end retail stores, and control rooms where reliability and image quality are paramount.','Standard Indoor LED Display P2.5 — Professional Choice for High-Definition Indoor Media','','publish','closed','closed','','standard-indoor-p2-5','','','2026-05-14 03:13:08','2026-05-14 03:13:08','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/standard-indoor-p2-5/',0,'product','',0),
(399,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:09','2026-05-14 03:13:09','The Standard Indoor P2 series is designed for fixed installation where high pixel density and superior color reproduction are required. It features a lightweight cabinet design that simplifies installation and maintenance.\n\nWith a pixel pitch of 2mm and a pixel density of 250,000 dot/m², it provides crisp visuals for close-range viewing. The cabinet resolution of 320×240px ensures high-fidelity playback of 2K/4K content.\n\nPerfect for corporate lobbies, high-end retail stores, and control rooms where reliability and image quality are paramount.','Standard Indoor LED Display P2 — Professional Choice for High-Definition Indoor Media','','publish','closed','closed','','standard-indoor-p2','','','2026-05-14 03:13:09','2026-05-14 03:13:09','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/standard-indoor-p2/',0,'product','',0),
(400,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:09','2026-05-14 03:13:09','The Standard Indoor P1.8 series is designed for fixed installation where high pixel density and superior color reproduction are required. It features a lightweight cabinet design that simplifies installation and maintenance.\n\nWith a pixel pitch of 1.86mm and a pixel density of 288,900 dot/m², it provides crisp visuals for close-range viewing. The cabinet resolution of 344×258px ensures high-fidelity playback of 2K/4K content.\n\nPerfect for corporate lobbies, high-end retail stores, and control rooms where reliability and image quality are paramount.','Standard Indoor LED Display P1.8 — Professional Choice for High-Definition Indoor Media','','publish','closed','closed','','standard-indoor-p1-8','','','2026-05-14 03:13:09','2026-05-14 03:13:09','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/standard-indoor-p1-8/',0,'product','',0),
(401,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:09','2026-05-14 03:13:09','The Standard Indoor P1.6 series is designed for fixed installation where high pixel density and superior color reproduction are required. It features a lightweight cabinet design that simplifies installation and maintenance.\n\nWith a pixel pitch of 1.66mm and a pixel density of 360,000 dot/m², it provides crisp visuals for close-range viewing. The cabinet resolution of 384×288px ensures high-fidelity playback of 2K/4K content.\n\nPerfect for corporate lobbies, high-end retail stores, and control rooms where reliability and image quality are paramount.','Standard Indoor LED Display P1.6 — Professional Choice for High-Definition Indoor Media','','publish','closed','closed','','standard-indoor-p1-6','','','2026-05-14 03:13:09','2026-05-14 03:13:09','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/standard-indoor-p1-6/',0,'product','',0),
(402,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:09','2026-05-14 03:13:09','The Standard Indoor P1.5 series is designed for fixed installation where high pixel density and superior color reproduction are required. It features a lightweight cabinet design that simplifies installation and maintenance.\n\nWith a pixel pitch of 1.53mm and a pixel density of 422,500 dot/m², it provides crisp visuals for close-range viewing. The cabinet resolution of 416×312px ensures high-fidelity playback of 2K/4K content.\n\nPerfect for corporate lobbies, high-end retail stores, and control rooms where reliability and image quality are paramount.','Standard Indoor LED Display P1.5 — Professional Choice for High-Definition Indoor Media','','publish','closed','closed','','standard-indoor-p1-5','','','2026-05-14 03:13:09','2026-05-14 03:13:09','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/standard-indoor-p1-5/',0,'product','',0),
(403,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:09','2026-05-14 03:13:09','The Standard Indoor P1.3 series is designed for fixed installation where high pixel density and superior color reproduction are required. It features a lightweight cabinet design that simplifies installation and maintenance.\n\nWith a pixel pitch of 1.37mm and a pixel density of 525,625 dot/m², it provides crisp visuals for close-range viewing. The cabinet resolution of 464×348px ensures high-fidelity playback of 2K/4K content.\n\nPerfect for corporate lobbies, high-end retail stores, and control rooms where reliability and image quality are paramount.','Standard Indoor LED Display P1.3 — Professional Choice for High-Definition Indoor Media','','publish','closed','closed','','standard-indoor-p1-3','','','2026-05-14 03:13:09','2026-05-14 03:13:09','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/standard-indoor-p1-3/',0,'product','',0),
(404,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:09','2026-05-14 03:13:09','The Standard Indoor P1.2 series is designed for fixed installation where high pixel density and superior color reproduction are required. It features a lightweight cabinet design that simplifies installation and maintenance.\n\nWith a pixel pitch of 1.25mm and a pixel density of 640,000 dot/m², it provides crisp visuals for close-range viewing. The cabinet resolution of 512×376px ensures high-fidelity playback of 2K/4K content.\n\nPerfect for corporate lobbies, high-end retail stores, and control rooms where reliability and image quality are paramount.','Standard Indoor LED Display P1.2 — Professional Choice for High-Definition Indoor Media','','publish','closed','closed','','standard-indoor-p1-2','','','2026-05-14 03:13:09','2026-05-14 03:13:09','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/standard-indoor-p1-2/',0,'product','',0),
(405,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:09','2026-05-14 03:13:09','The COB-P1.5 adopts RGB flip-chip COB encapsulation technology, delivering superior thermal management and stability compared to traditional SMD displays. With 1.56mm pixel pitch and 10,000:1 contrast ratio, it produces stunning image quality for premium indoor environments.\n\nFeaturing a 600×337.5mm cabinet in 16:9 ratio with 384×216px resolution per cabinet, the display supports seamless tiling for 4K and beyond. Brightness is adjustable from 0-800 nit with a refresh rate of ≥3840Hz for flicker-free camera-friendly display.\n\nIdeal for high-end conference rooms, broadcast studios, command centers, and exhibition halls where ultra-fine pixel pitch and professional image quality are essential.','COB Series COB-P1.5 Indoor LED Display — Ultra Fine Pitch, 10000:1 Contrast','','publish','closed','closed','','cob-p1-5','','','2026-05-14 03:13:09','2026-05-14 03:13:09','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/cob-p1-5/',0,'product','',0),
(406,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:09','2026-05-14 03:13:09','The COB-P1.2 adopts RGB flip-chip COB encapsulation technology, delivering superior thermal management and stability compared to traditional SMD displays. With 1.25mm pixel pitch and 10,000:1 contrast ratio, it produces stunning image quality for premium indoor environments.\n\nFeaturing a 600×337.5mm cabinet in 16:9 ratio with 480×270px resolution per cabinet, the display supports seamless tiling for 4K and beyond. Brightness is adjustable from 0-800 nit with a refresh rate of ≥3840Hz for flicker-free camera-friendly display.\n\nIdeal for high-end conference rooms, broadcast studios, command centers, and exhibition halls where ultra-fine pixel pitch and professional image quality are essential.','COB Series COB-P1.2 Indoor LED Display — Ultra Fine Pitch, 10000:1 Contrast','','publish','closed','closed','','cob-p1-2','','','2026-05-14 03:13:09','2026-05-14 03:13:09','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/cob-p1-2/',0,'product','',0),
(407,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:10','2026-05-14 03:13:10','The COB-P0.9 adopts RGB flip-chip COB encapsulation technology, delivering superior thermal management and stability compared to traditional SMD displays. With 0.93mm pixel pitch and 10,000:1 contrast ratio, it produces stunning image quality for premium indoor environments.\n\nFeaturing a 600×337.5mm cabinet in 16:9 ratio with 640×360px resolution per cabinet, the display supports seamless tiling for 4K and beyond. Brightness is adjustable from 0-800 nit with a refresh rate of ≥3840Hz for flicker-free camera-friendly display.\n\nIdeal for high-end conference rooms, broadcast studios, command centers, and exhibition halls where ultra-fine pixel pitch and professional image quality are essential.','COB Series COB-P0.9 Indoor LED Display — Ultra Fine Pitch, 10000:1 Contrast','','publish','closed','closed','','cob-p0-9','','','2026-05-14 03:13:10','2026-05-14 03:13:10','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/cob-p0-9/',0,'product','',0),
(408,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:10','2026-05-14 03:13:10','The COB-P0.7 adopts RGB flip-chip COB encapsulation technology, delivering superior thermal management and stability compared to traditional SMD displays. With 0.78mm pixel pitch and 10,000:1 contrast ratio, it produces stunning image quality for premium indoor environments.\n\nFeaturing a 600×337.5mm cabinet in 16:9 ratio with 768×432px resolution per cabinet, the display supports seamless tiling for 4K and beyond. Brightness is adjustable from 0-800 nit with a refresh rate of ≥3840Hz for flicker-free camera-friendly display.\n\nIdeal for high-end conference rooms, broadcast studios, command centers, and exhibition halls where ultra-fine pixel pitch and professional image quality are essential.','COB Series COB-P0.7 Indoor LED Display — Ultra Fine Pitch, 10000:1 Contrast','','publish','closed','closed','','cob-p0-7','','','2026-05-14 03:13:10','2026-05-14 03:13:10','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/cob-p0-7/',0,'product','',0),
(409,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:10','2026-05-14 03:13:10','Designed for 16:9 aspect ratio standard, the 16:9 Indoor P0.9 series allows users to build HD/4K/8K video walls without any image distortion. Its rigid connection system ensures perfect alignment across multiple cabinets.\n\nWith 0.93mm pixel pitch, it offers exceptional clarity for high-end presentation environments. The 600x337.5mm or 640x360mm cabinet sizes are optimized for standard mounting systems.\n\nIdeally suited for conference centers, boardrooms, and digital cinema applications.','16:9 Indoor LED Display P0.9 — Seamless 4K/8K Video Wall Solution','','publish','closed','closed','','169-indoor-p0-9','','','2026-05-14 03:13:10','2026-05-14 03:13:10','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/169-indoor-p0-9/',0,'product','',0),
(410,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:10','2026-05-14 03:13:10','Designed for 16:9 aspect ratio standard, the 16:9 Indoor P1.25 series allows users to build HD/4K/8K video walls without any image distortion. Its rigid connection system ensures perfect alignment across multiple cabinets.\n\nWith 1.25mm pixel pitch, it offers exceptional clarity for high-end presentation environments. The 600x337.5mm or 640x360mm cabinet sizes are optimized for standard mounting systems.\n\nIdeally suited for conference centers, boardrooms, and digital cinema applications.','16:9 Indoor LED Display P1.25 — Seamless 4K/8K Video Wall Solution','','publish','closed','closed','','169-indoor-p1-25','','','2026-05-14 03:13:10','2026-05-14 03:13:10','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/169-indoor-p1-25/',0,'product','',0),
