(423,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:11','2026-05-14 03:13:11','The Rental Indoor P2.6 series is optimized for the demanding event industry. It features an ultra-lightweight magnesium alloy cabinet and quick-lock system for fast assembly by a single person.\n\nWith 2.6mm pixel pitch, it delivers sharp visuals for stage backdrops and live events. The 500x500mm or 500x1000mm cabinet sizes provide maximum configuration flexibility.\n\nIdeal for concerts, trade shows, corporate events, and wedding stages.','Rental LED Screen Indoor P2.6 — Quick Setup, High Stability for Events','','publish','closed','closed','','rental-indoor-p2-6','','','2026-06-16 16:17:06','2026-06-16 16:17:06','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/rental-indoor-p2-6/',0,'product','',0),
(424,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:11','2026-05-14 03:13:11','The Rental Indoor P2.9 series is optimized for the demanding event industry. It features an ultra-lightweight magnesium alloy cabinet and quick-lock system for fast assembly by a single person.\n\nWith 2.9mm pixel pitch, it delivers sharp visuals for stage backdrops and live events. The 500x500mm or 500x1000mm cabinet sizes provide maximum configuration flexibility.\n\nIdeal for concerts, trade shows, corporate events, and wedding stages.','Rental LED Screen Indoor P2.9 — Quick Setup, High Stability for Events','','publish','closed','closed','','rental-indoor-p2-9','','','2026-06-16 16:17:06','2026-06-16 16:17:06','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/rental-indoor-p2-9/',0,'product','',0),
(425,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:11','2026-05-14 03:13:11','<p>Our Indoor Stage Rental LED Screen P3.91 is a high-performance, high-definition rental display system engineered for concerts, corporate conferences, product launches, weddings, and exhibition spaces. Built with a high-precision, lightweight die-cast aluminum cabinet structure, it enables fast, single-person installation and dismantling, significantly reducing labor and setup times.</p>\n<h2>High-Precision Die-cast Aluminum &amp; Fast Setup</h2>\n<p>The cabinet dimension is 500×500 mm with a slim 75 mm thickness, weighing only 7.5 kg per panel. Exceptional manufacturing tolerance guarantees a completely flat and seamless visual surface. Equipped with industrial-grade positioning pins and ergonomic quick-locks on both sides, a single technician can lock panels together within 3 seconds. It supports truss-hanging up to 15 panels high or ground-stacking on stable stage bases.</p>\n<h2>Toolless Front &amp; Rear Maintenance</h2>\n<p>Featuring a dual-access design, the magnetic modules can be serviced from the front (using a suction tool) or rear. The independent power and control box features a modular, plug-and-play design that can be swapped out in 10 seconds without tools. This double maintenance channel ensures quick replacements during live broadcasts, ensuring zero broadcast interruptions.</p>\n<h2>Outstanding Visuals &amp; Safety Protections</h2>\n<p>Equipped with a high-refresh driver IC (≥3840Hz) and 14-bit grayscale processing, the display ensures smooth, flicker-free imagery with no scanning lines under professional camera lenses and mobile phones. Built-in fold-out corner guards protect the edge LEDs from physical impact when the cabinet is placed on the floor during staging operations.</p>','Stage Rental LED Screen Indoor P3.91 — High Precision & Quick Setup for Events','Saves time and labor, easy to install. High brightness, high grayscale, high refresh rate, high-definition and delicate. Meets the requirements of hanging and stacking installation, and satisfies both indoor and outdoor requirements. The PCB adopts a high-strength anti-collision pad design, which can withstand an impact of 8kg without fear of dead or dropped lights. The cabinet is thin and light, making disassembly, assembly, and transportation easy, reducing product thickness and saving screen space. Precise, fast, and flexible positioning installation can effectively respond to different application fields.','publish','closed','closed','','rental-indoor-p3-91','','','2026-06-16 16:17:06','2026-06-16 16:17:06','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/rental-indoor-p3-9/',0,'product','',0),
(426,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:12','2026-05-14 03:13:12','The Rental Indoor P4.8 series is optimized for the demanding event industry. It features an ultra-lightweight magnesium alloy cabinet and quick-lock system for fast assembly by a single person.\n\nWith 4.8mm pixel pitch, it delivers sharp visuals for stage backdrops and live events. The 500x500mm or 500x1000mm cabinet sizes provide maximum configuration flexibility.\n\nIdeal for concerts, trade shows, corporate events, and wedding stages.','Rental LED Screen Indoor P4.8 — Quick Setup, High Stability for Events','','publish','closed','closed','','rental-indoor-p4-8','','','2026-06-16 16:17:06','2026-06-16 16:17:06','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/rental-indoor-p4-8/',0,'product','',0),
(427,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:12','2026-05-14 03:13:12','The Rental Outdoor P2.9 series is optimized for the demanding event industry. It features an ultra-lightweight magnesium alloy cabinet and quick-lock system for fast assembly by a single person.\n\nWith 2.9mm pixel pitch, it delivers sharp visuals for stage backdrops and live events. The 500x500mm or 500x1000mm cabinet sizes provide maximum configuration flexibility.\n\nIdeal for concerts, trade shows, corporate events, and wedding stages.','Rental LED Screen Outdoor P2.9 — Quick Setup, High Stability for Events','','publish','closed','closed','','rental-outdoor-p2-9','','','2026-06-16 16:17:06','2026-06-16 16:17:06','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/rental-outdoor-p2-9/',0,'product','',0),
(428,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:12','2026-05-14 03:13:12','<p>Our All-Weather Outdoor Stage Rental LED Screen P3.91 is a robust, high-performance display solution specifically built for outdoor music festivals, live sporting broadcasts, outdoor theaters, and corporate events. The dustproof and waterproof die-cast aluminum cabinet is engineered to withstand extreme weather conditions while offering lightweight convenience and high-speed assembly.</p>\n<h2>IP65 Rated Die-cast Aluminum &amp; Anti-Wind Design</h2>\n<p>Manufactured with high-strength die-cast aluminum, the 500×500 mm cabinet is extremely durable, weighing only 7.5 kg with a thickness of 75 mm. It achieves an IP65 ingress protection rating (dustproof and water-jet resistant) on both front and rear faces, securing operations during sudden rainstorms. Heavy-duty quick locks provide superior pull load limits, maintaining seamless connections even under heavy wind loads.</p>\n<h2>Superb Brightness &amp; Sunlight Readability</h2>\n<p>Featuring premium outdoor SMD LEDs, the screen delivers a white balance brightness of ≥4500 nits (up to 5500 nits), retaining high contrast and vibrant color saturation under direct sunlight. With a high refresh rate of ≥3840Hz and a wide viewing angle, it delivers a flicker-free, immersive viewing experience to large audiences across expansive outdoor arenas.</p>\n<h2>Dual-Access Service &amp; Folding Corner Guards</h2>\n<p>The display supports toolless module removal from both the front and rear. The power control enclosure is fully sealed for waterproof security yet features quick-release handles for toolless hot-swapping in 10 seconds. Built-in folding corner guards lift the bottom modules off the ground during setup, securing the delicate edge LEDs from drag and collision damages.</p>','Stage Rental LED Screen Outdoor P3.91 — All-Weather High Brightness Event Display','All-weather Stage Rental LED Display P3.91 features an IP65 waterproof rated die-cast aluminum cabinet (7.5kg), high brightness ≥4500 nit, and quick-lock mechanism. Engineered for outdoor music festivals, sporting events, and cultural tourism.','publish','closed','closed','','rental-outdoor-p3-91','','','2026-06-16 16:17:06','2026-06-16 16:17:06','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/rental-outdoor-p3-9/',0,'product','',0),
