(450,0,'2026-05-14 03:13:14','2026-05-14 03:13:14','<p>Our Flexible LED Soft Module is a high-performance, creatively adaptable display solution designed for architectural contours and creative staging. Engineered with a premium silicone/rubber soft chassis, the modules can bend, twist, and wrap around columns or curved surfaces with exceptional ease.</p>\n<h3>Rubber Base &amp; Mask with Perfect Bending</h3>\n<p>The combination of a high-flexibility PCB and a specialized rubber bottom shell allows free bending. It supports a minimum installation diameter of just 406.6mm (using four 320x160mm modules to form a perfect circle), or infinite seamless splicing for customized columns, ribbons, inside/outside curves, and wave shapes.</p>\n<h3>Dedicated Anti-Ghosting Circuitry</h3>\n<p>Built with advanced scanning delay discharge compensation and a dedicated ghost-elimination circuit, the display guarantees highly clean, sharp, and drag-free visual performance. It reproduces rich, high-contrast colors and deep grayscales, ensuring perfect video playback without lag or visual distortion.</p>\n<h3>Magnetic Front Access &amp; Easy Mounting</h3>\n<p>Designed for fast and convenient servicing, the module features a strong magnetic front-access layout. Technicians can easily remove the modules from the front using specialized vacuum magnetic suction tools, making maintenance and installation in narrow or curved structures exceptionally simple. It supports modular paste mounting, hanging, or floor installation.</p>','Flexible LED Module P1.2 — Create Arches, Columns, and Curved Displays','Premium Flexible LED Soft Module features a high-flexibility rubber base and mask for creative curved designs (minimum 406.6mm cylinder diameter). Built with magnetic front-access maintenance and dedicated anti-ghosting circuits, delivering seamless, flicker-free, 360° all-around visuals for columns, arches, ribbons, and wave-shaped screens.','publish','closed','closed','','flex-p1-2','','','2026-05-14 03:13:14','2026-05-14 03:13:14','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/flex-p1-2/',0,'product','',0),
