(856,0,'2026-06-16 07:44:50','2026-06-16 07:44:50','<p>Our Smart Mobile LED Poster Screen is a next-generation high-definition digital signage solution designed to maximize advertising impact in high-traffic commercial environments. Built with a lightweight, high-tensile aluminum alloy frame, it combines a sleek, ultra-slim profile with extreme structural durability.</p>\n<h2>Lightweight Aluminum Mobile Design &amp; Easy Setup</h2>\n<p>Featuring a slim 60mm borderless casing, the poster display is exceptionally thin. The base is integrated with heavy-duty lockable rolling caster wheels and a fold-out kickstand, allowing a single person to easily push, park, and deploy the screen without installation. It supports multiple installation options: floor-standing with kickstand, vertical hanging from trusses, wall-mounting, or multi-screen seamless splicing.</p>\n<h2>Smart Cloud Clustering &amp; Content Control</h2>\n<p>The system is powered by an advanced multimedia controller that supports Wi-Fi, 4G, USB playback, and HDMI input. With smart cloud clustering control, marketing managers can update content, schedules, and screen states across multiple poster screens globally through a single centralized dashboard. The plug-and-play USB feature allows offline content loop playback, ensuring zero downtime even without network coverage.</p>\n<h2>Outstanding High-Definition Specifications</h2>\n<p>Equipped with premium P1.86 fine pitch LEDs (288,900 dots/m²) and a high refresh rate of ≥3840Hz, the display guarantees flicker-free visuals under phone cameras and professional studio broadcasting. A brightness level of 800 - 1200 nits ensures clear readability under bright indoor ambient lights, while the wide 160-degree viewing angle attracts audiences from all directions.</p>','Smart Mobile LED Poster Screen P2.0 — High-Definition Indoor Digital Signage','Premium High-Definition Mobile LED Poster Screen P1.86 features an ultra-slim aluminum cabinet (45kg complete unit) with built-in castor wheels and kickstand. Engineered with smart cloud clustering control, USB offline playback, and 1200 nit brightness. The ideal plug-and-play digital signage for retail shops, hotels, exhibitions, and flagship store fronts.','publish','closed','closed','','smart-mobile-led-poster-screen-p20','','','2026-06-16 16:17:06','2026-06-16 16:17:06','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/smart-mobile-led-poster-screen/',0,'product','',0),
(857,0,'2026-06-16 07:44:50','2026-06-16 07:44:50','<p>中茗光电智能移动式 LED 海报屏是专为高流量商业环境设计的新一代高清数字标牌解决方案。该产品采用轻量化、高强度的铝合金边框制造，集纤薄的侧面轮廓与卓越的结构耐用性于一体。</p>\n<h2>超薄美学外框与便捷移动免安装</h2>\n<p>机身外框厚度仅为 60mm，采用黑色磨砂阳极氧化铝合金边框，实现正面全面屏显示视觉效果。底座集成高负重静音带锁万向轮和折叠式背置支架，单人即推即走、随停随放，免去传统拼接大屏繁琐的安装调试过程。支持地拖折叠立装、舞台吊装及壁挂级联。</p>\n<h2>智能云端集群控制与多屏 HDMI 拼接</h2>\n<p>系统搭载先进的多媒体播放控制器，支持 Wi-Fi、4G 移动网络、USB 即插即播及 HDMI 输入。通过智能云集群控制，企划人员可通过单个网页或手机 App 云后台，全球同步更新成百上千台海报屏的画面与亮度。支持多屏级联无缝拼接，仅需 HDMI 线连接，6 台海报屏即可合二为一，拼装成一面标准 16:9 2K 视频墙，无需拼接处理器。</p>\n<h2>高清 P1.86 微间距显示与便捷维护</h2>\n<p>采用高品质 SMD/GOB 高清微间距模组，像素密度达 288,900 像素/m²。近距离阅读文字时清晰锐利，能完美呈现高对比度视频广告。搭载 ≥3840Hz 高刷新率芯片与前维护磁吸设计，手机拍照无频闪条纹，模组维护极速简单。</p>','智能移动式 LED 海报屏 P2.0 — 高清室内数字标牌广告机','高端室内高清移动式 LED 海报屏 P1.86，采用超薄铝合金外框（整机重45kg），自带万向滚轮和折叠支架。集成智能云端集群控制、USB离线循环播放、1200nit亮度。适用于零售店铺、酒店大堂、大型展览及品牌旗舰店。','publish','closed','closed','','smart-mobile-led-poster-screen-p20-zh','','','2026-06-16 16:17:06','2026-06-16 16:17:06','',0,'https://[PRODUCTION_DOMAIN]/products/smart-mobile-led-poster-screen-zh/',0,'product','',0),
